snippet.title: Best CHILDHOOD MADNESS moments! 50+ FUNNIEST clips, lots of LAUGHING!
snippet.description:
Childhood moments can be so cool! This is a mixture of more than 50 clips of pure kid madness, which kicks in at our younger ages and creates so many funny memories to remember! Which is yours favourite one? Hope you like our video mix, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

The content in this video is licensed and used with authorization of the rights holder. If you have any questions about compilation or clip licensing, please contact us: tigerlicensing@gmail.com
